beer.beer_name: Alpha Daydream Fresh Hop Hazy IPA
beer.beer_description:
Hops: Single Hop Nectaron
Malts: Lager Light, Oats, Big O, Gladiator

Once every year at hop harvest time, our brew team has the privilege to work with
freshly harvested green hops. This year we bring you a full-bodied Hazy IPA brewed with whole-cone Necatron® hops. Intense flavour, aromas of passionfruit, peach, grapefruit, and pineapple.
Thanks to the crew in the top of the South for putting out the best hops in the world.
